snippet.title: Capsule Lock - Android Gameplay (Isometric Puzzle Game)
snippet.description:
Download game "Capsule Lock" for free and try to solve all of the 48 puzzles on the way. Game is currently available on Android devices through itch.io website. Playtime: Around 2 hours. Game is made in Unity.  

Game link: https://bandraxgaming.itch.io/capsule-lock

Itch.io link: https://bandraxgaming.itch.io/

Enjoy!
